<body>

    <h1>Phillip’s Pressure Warriors</h1>
    <p><strong>We are hiring at this time.</strong> We clean the hardest things. Don’t worry — we have power washers to clean cars.</p>

    <!-- SERVICES -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Services</h2>
        <p>Below is a full list of our services and pricing. Prices may vary depending on size, dirt level, and difficulty.</p>

        <h3>Trip & Fuel Costs</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Travel / Gas Fee: $10–$20 (distance-based)</li>
            <li>Equipment Fuel Cost: $5 per job</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Vehicle Exterior Cleaning</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Car Exterior Wash: $25</li>
            <li>Truck / SUV Exterior Wash: $35</li>
            <li>Full Detail Add‑On: +$15</li>
            <li>Rims & Tire Shine: +$15</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Home Exterior Services</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>House Siding Wash: $80–$150 (size‑based)</li>
            <li>Driveway Cleaning: $40–$75 (size & dirt‑based)</li>
            <li>Sidewalk / Walkway Cleaning: $15–$30</li>
            <li>Deck / Porch Cleaning: $30–$60</li>
            <li>Fence Cleaning: $25–$50</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Gutter Services</h3>
        <p><em>We rarely offer gutter services.</em></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Gutter Exterior Wash: $25–$40</li>
            <li>Gutter Interior Clean: $40–$60</li>
            <li>Downspout Flush: $10</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Window Cleaning</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Exterior Window Wash: $30–$60</li>
            <li>Full Home Window Package: $60–$120</li>
            <li>Screen Cleaning Add‑On: +$10</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Add‑On Services</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Mold / Mildew Treatment: $10–$20</li>
            <li>Oil Stain Removal: +$15</li>
            <li>Patio / Concrete Pad Cleaning: $20–$40</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTRACT REQUIREMENT -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Contract Requirement</h2>
        <p>
            Before ANY job begins, you <strong>MUST</strong> sign a service contract.  
            <strong>No exceptions.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            If you do not sign the contract, we will not clean your house, car, gutters, windows, or any service you request.
        </p>
        <p>
            This protects both you and FTSW by making sure every job has clear expectations, agreed pricing, and documented approval.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you do not understand the contract, we will read it to you and explain it part by part.  
            If you refuse to sign or say “I’ll sign after,” we will NOT perform the job.
        </p>
        <p><strong>No signature, no service. — Owner: Phillip Hibbets</strong></p>
    </div>

    <!-- BOOKING FORM -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Book Your Service</h2>
        <form action="#" method="POST">
            <label>First & Last Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required>

            <label>Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required>

            <label>Your Message</label>
            <textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Submit Booking Request</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTACT INFO -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 319-217-2874</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> phillipspressurewarriors@gmail.com</p>
    </div>

</body>
